# Project Overview

This is svelte & svelte-kit based commnity

- Frontend: svelete5 + TypeScript
- Backend: sveltekit2 + Prisma + mongodb
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui

## Essential Elements

- Always include error handling with try-catch
- Use Zod for runtime validation
- Include TypeScript interfaces for all props
- Add JSDoc comments for complex functions

# Deprecated Patterns - DO NOT USE

❌ Class components (use functional components)
❌ var declarations (use const/let)
❌ any type (use proper TypeScript types)

## Preferred Patterns

✅ Arrow functions for components
✅ Custom hooks for state logic
✅ Strict TypeScript configurations

## Migraiton Rule

- ckeditor 최신 안정화 버전으로 변경
- Database model 구조는 변경하지 않음

변경후에는 커밋을 해줍니다.
